title: Emily Ratajkowski and Bella Hadid Are Making the Naked Vacation Instagram a Thing
text: Emily Ratajkowski and Bella Hadid Are Making the Naked Vacation Instagram a Thing Most Popular By Alyssa Bailey Mar 20, 2017 Currently, beautiful humans Emily Ratajkowski and Bella Hadid are away in paradise—apart but united in the kind of naked receipts they're sharing of their travels. They both just posted pics of themselves in the nearly nude. Hadid shared several of herself wearing a one-piece so stringy and skin-tone, it's like there's nothing there: ❤ A post shared by Bella Hadid (@bellahadid) on Mar 19, 2017 at 8:32pm PDT Advertisement   A post shared by Bella Hadid (@bellahadid) on Mar 19, 2017 at 9:17pm PDT Most Popular A post shared by Bella Hadid (@bellahadid) on Mar 19, 2017 at 7:21pm PDT And Emrata went for the full naked shot on the rocks in Mexico: A post shared by Emily Ratajkowski (@emrata) on Mar 19, 2017 at 1:11pm PDT The two also shared traditional bikini pics: A post shared by Bella Hadid (@bellahadid) on Mar 19, 2017 at 10:33am PDT A post shared by Emily Ratajkowski (@emrata) on Mar 19, 2017 at 7:59am PDT And Emrata gave a friendly reminder that not even supermodels are immune to sunburn: A post shared by Emily Ratajkowski (@emrata) on Mar 20, 2017 at 8:11am PDT Lather up, folks.
